abort.cannot_connect:
Couldn't open a Bluetooth connection to {address}.

Detail: {error}

Make sure the shade is in pairing mode (PAIR button) and that a Bluetooth proxy is online and within range.

abort.pairing_failed_auth:
Pairing failed with an authentication error. The shade may already be bonded to another adapter, or the bond table is full.

Detail: {error}

To recover: factory-reset the shade by holding the PAIR button until the LED flashes rapidly, then try adding it again.

abort.pairing_failed:
Pairing with {address} failed.

Detail: {error}

Make sure the shade is in pairing mode (PAIR button) and try again.
